    <div class="space">
      <section class="bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-t-2xl shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Order Processing</h2>
        <p>We strive to process and ship all orders within 48-72 working hours from the time the order is successfully placed. Please note that orders placed on weekends or public holidays will be processed on the next working day.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Shipping & Delivery</h2>
        <ul class="custom-bullet space-y-1">
          <li>All packages are shipped with proper labels and secure seals to ensure the safety of your order.</li>
          <li>Once your order is dispatched, you will receive a tracking number via email or WhatsApp to monitor the delivery status.</li>
          <li>Delivery timelines may vary based on your location and the courier service used. Estimated delivery times will be provided at checkout.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-900 p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Shipping Partners</h2>
        <p>We partner with reliable courier services to ensure timely and safe delivery of your order.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Shipping Charges</h2>
        <ul class="custom-bullet space-y-1">
          <li>We offer free shipping on all orders within India.</li>
          <li>Any additional customs duties, taxes, or import charges (for international orders) will be the responsibility of the customer.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-900 p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Address Accuracy</h2>
        <p>Customers are requested to provide accurate and complete shipping details. We are not responsible for orders delayed or undelivered due to incorrect or incomplete addresses.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">6. Order Tracking</h2>
        <p>Once your order is dispatched, you can track its status using the provided tracking number on our courier partner's website.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-900 p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">7. Delays & Exceptions</h2>
        <p>While we aim to meet the estimated delivery timelines, delays due to unforeseen circumstances such as weather conditions, strikes, or logistical issues may occur. We appreciate your patience in such cases.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-bl-xl rounded-br-xl shadow-lg mb-12">
